<subSubSection id="C306789DFFCDFF9C6BB0F8E0FBAFF8CA" pageId="7" pageNumber="572" type="reference_group">
<paragraph id="8BA32B16FFCDFF9C6BB0F8E0FBAFF8CA" blockId="7.[151,1436,1837,1890]" pageId="7" pageNumber="572">
<treatmentCitationGroup id="AB0C0C38FFCDFF9C6BB0F8E0FBAFF8CA" pageId="7" pageNumber="572">
<treatmentCitation id="0ABD0D07FFCDFF9C6BB0F8E0FD14F8EB" author="Santschi, F." box="[151,714,1837,1859]" page="229" pageId="7" pageNumber="572" year="1927">
<taxonomicName id="4C1C5095FFCDFF9C6BB0F8E0FD14F8EB" authority="Santschi, 1927: 229" authorityName="Santschi" authorityPageNumber="229" authorityYear="1927" box="[151,714,1837,1859]" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Messor" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="572" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="variety" species="semirufus" variety="ebeninus">
<emphasis id="B968F704FFCDFF9C6BB0F8E0FE39F8EB" box="[151,487,1837,1859]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="572">Messor semirufus var. ebeninus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EF8D56E7FFCDFF9C6AD4F8E3FD14F8EB" author="Santschi, F." box="[499,714,1837,1859]" pageId="7" pageNumber="572" pagination="225 - 250" refId="ref8101" refString="Santschi, F. (1927) Revision des Messor du groupe instabilis Sm. Boletin de la Real Sociedad Espanola de Historia Natural, 27, 225 - 250." type="journal article" year="1927">Santschi, 1927: 229</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
</treatmentCitation>
. Raised to species: 
<treatmentCitation id="0ABD0D07FFCDFF9C6881F8E3FBB3F8EB" box="[934,1133,1837,1859]" pageId="7" pageNumber="572">Tohmé, 1971: 569</treatmentCitation>
. Junior synonym of 
<treatmentCitation id="0ABD0D07FFCDFF9C6E76F8E0FDE2F8CA" author="Baroni Urbani, C." page="227" pageId="7" pageNumber="572" year="1974">
<taxonomicName id="4C1C5095FFCDFF9C6E76F8E0FDE2F8CA" authority=": Baroni Urbani, 1974: 227" authorityName="Baroni Urbani" authorityPageNumber="227" authorityYear="1974" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Messor" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="572" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="semirufus">
<emphasis id="B968F704FFCDFF9C6E76F8E0FEF4F8CA" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="572">Messor semirufus</emphasis>
: 
<bibRefCitation id="EF8D56E7FFCDFF9C6A1FF882FDE2F8CA" author="Baroni Urbani, C." box="[312,572,1868,1890]" pageId="7" pageNumber="572" pagination="225 - 252" refId="ref6178" refString="Baroni Urbani, C. (1974) Studi sulla mirmecofauna d'Italia. XII. Le Isole Pontine. Fragmenta Entomologica, 9, 225 - 252." type="journal article" year="1974">Baroni Urbani, 1974: 227</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
</treatmentCitation>
. Revived from synonymy: 
<treatmentCitation id="0ABD0D07FFCDFF9C6875F882FBAFF8CA" box="[850,1137,1868,1890]" pageId="7" pageNumber="572">Tohmé &amp; Tohmé, 1981:142.</treatmentCitation>
</treatmentCitationGroup>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C306789DFFCDFF9C6BB0F840FE55F847" pageId="7" pageNumber="572" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BA32B16FFCDFF9C6BB0F840FE55F847" blockId="7.[151,1436,1934,2031]" pageId="7" pageNumber="572">
This species is widely distributed throughout the Arabian Peninsula (
<bibRefCitation id="EF8D56E7FFCDFF9C68BDF840FBA9F80F" author="Collingwood, C. A." box="[922,1143,1934,1959]" pageId="7" pageNumber="572" pagination="230 - 302" refId="ref6815" refString="Collingwood, C. A. (1985) Hymenoptera: Fam. Formicidae of Saudi Arabia. Fauna Saudi Arabia, 7, 230 - 302." type="journal article" year="1985">Collingwood, 1985</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EF8D56E7FFCDFF9C6FA5F840FF0DF863" author="Collingwood, C. A. &amp; Agosti, D." pageId="7" pageNumber="572" pagination="300 - 385" refId="ref6843" refString="Collingwood, C. A. &amp; Agosti, D. (1996) Formicidae of Saudi Arabia (Part 2). Fauna of Saudi Arabia, 15, 300 - 385." type="journal article" year="1996">Collingwood and Agosti, 1996</bibRefCitation>
). At Rawdhat Khorim, worker activity has two peaks of abundance, in April and December, decreasing from July through October.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
